Wenzel’s Audio Circuits — Licensing Information
===============================================

This repository contains two categories of content, each under its own license:

1.  Hardware design files (KiCad projects, schematics, PCB layouts, footprints,
    3D models, and PDF/PNG renders of schematics and boards) are licensed under:

        CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 – Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S-2.0)

    SPDX-License-Identifier: CERN-OHL-S-2.0

    You may copy, modify, and distribute these design files provided that any
    modified versions and derivatives are also released under the same licence.

    Full text of the CERN-OHL-S-2.0 is included below.

2.  Supporting software, scripts, and configuration files (for example Nix
    configurations, Bash scripts, or other utility code) are licensed under:

        The MIT License

    SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT

    Full text of the MIT License follows the CERN-OHL-S-2.0 text.

